high_descs: Turn to the right to face the bread on the counter next to the microwave.
Pick the bread up from off of the counter top.
Turn to the right then go straight and to the left to face the black refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bread inside, close the refrigerator, wait a few seconds, open the refrigerator, pick up the bread, and close the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk towards the white table.
Place the bread on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place the refrigerated bread on the white table in the corner of the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn right, go to counter with bread on it.
Pick up bread from between microwave and green sponge.
Turn right, go towards wall.  Turn left and face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put bread on top shelf, close refrigerator.  Open refrigerator, take bread out, close refrigerator.
Place bread on left lower corner of table, below and to the left of the cup, to the left of spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put bread in refrigerator, take it back out and put on table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to face the counter where the bread is.
Pick the bread up from the counter.
Go right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge and shut the door, then open the door and pick the bread up again and shut the fridge door.
Turn around and go forward to stand in front of the white table.
Put the bread on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled loaf of bread on a table.
